      "message": "nit:\n\n\txv :\u003d x.Int\n\tyv :\u003d y\n\tif y, ok :\u003d y.(duration); ok {\n\t\tyv \u003d y.Int\n\t}\n\tzv, err :\u003d starlark.Binary(op, xv, yv)\n\tif err !\u003d nil {\n\t\treturn nil, err\n\t}\n\tzn, err :\u003d starlark.NumberToInt(zv)\n\tif err !\u003d nil {\n\t\treturn nil, err\n\t}\n\treturn duration{zn}, nil\n\nis shorter and supports `1.5 * time.hour`",
